name: Cardio Babies Bundle
description:
For those CHD families!  1 out of 100 babies born have a heart defect of some kind.  Most of these conditions need N.I.C.U. help.  We now have a bundle just for these babies.  There are 8 pages that include... My Heart, My Diagnosis, Images of My Heart, My Specialists, Procedures (2 pages) and Surgery (2 pages).  Each page has a bible verses included in the design to encourage the families thru this hard time.  There is currently one design.  The colors will blend with any Dreemie Preemie book design but go very well with the Stripes and Dots Collection.  

***NOTE*** Scrapbook not included.  Product includes 12 x 12 pages that are bundled together so you can create your own book. The pages fit any 12 x 12 scrapbook that you can purchase at any hobby or department store. It’s wonderful… that way you can incorporate your own scrapbook pages into this grouping or omit pages that don’t fit your babies story.

name: Isolette Bumpers
description:
12x 4 cards (16 cards in all). Give a smile to NICU parents, nurses, and have fun with your baby. Inspired by bumper stickers on cars but made for isolette.

OH, what fun. Just because the NICU is sometimes scary doesn’t mean you can’t have some fun. Share a smile with your baby, your nurses and doctors and add some humor for the other parents around you.  to Share a smile with your baby, nurses, doctors and add some humor for the other parents around you.
Might as well make the best of things by playing with your Dreemie Preemie. Cards included are… My Mommy held me today- My Daddy held me today- My Grandparents love me- I’m a little sister- I’m a little brother- I’m the Nurses’ Favorite Deal with it- I did something amazing today- I had a bath today, smell me- I’m a cuddle bug- This hat is smooching my hair- Try the Mama Milk, it’s great- I could model, I’m that cute- Anybody got a spoon, I found a tunnel out- I’m being prayed for at Dreemie Preemie.com- Be nice to me, I had a rough night- Sweet Dreemie Little Preemie
